TEXT -136 56 Left 2 !************************************************\n* Wide-Swing Cascode Current Mirror\n* Correct Topology - LTspice Compatible\n************************************************\n \n*************** SUPPLY *************************\nVDD vdd 0 1.8\nVOUT vo 0 0\n \n*************** MOS MODEL **********************\n.model nmos NMOS (\n+ LEVEL=1\n+ VTO=0.5\n+ KP=200u\n+ LAMBDA=0.02)\n \n*************** IDEAL BANDGAP ******************\n* 10 uA reference current\nIREF nref 0 DC 10u\n \n*************** BIAS VOLTAGES ******************\nVBN vbiasn 0 0.7\nVBC vbiasc 0 0.9\n \n*************** REFERENCE BRANCH ***************\nMREF nref vbiasn 0 0 nmos W=5u L=2u\nMCR  n1   vbiasc nref 0 nmos W=5u L=2u\n \n*************** OUTPUT BRANCH ******************\nM1  n2 vbiasn 0 0 nmos W=5u L=2u\nM4  vo vbiasc n2 0 nmos W=5u L=2u\n \n*************** ANALYSIS ***********************\n.dc VOUT 0 1 1m\n \n.end
